external_knowledge:
Case overview: a comprehensive view of a case, including its process ID, duration, status, creator, and activity statistics; 
Process ID: a unique identifier for a process;
Duration: the time period between the start and end times of a case;
Status: the current state of a case;
Creator: the user who created a case;
Cumulative probability: the sum of the probabilities of all activities in a case;
Total activities: the number of activities in a case;
Average activity probability: the average probability of all activities in a case;
Current status: the latest status of a case;
Last modifier: the user who last modified a case;
Modification timestamp: the timestamp when a case was last modified.
